330
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,820
13B.

331
00:26:08,650 --> 00:26:09,490
Fahim Nasir.

332
00:26:09,520 --> 00:26:12,020
<i>Ông đang hết thời gian.</i>

333
00:26:12,610 --> 00:26:13,610
5B.

